summary: This code sets up a directory for dependencies, navigates to the MiraiGo folder, and configures the GOPATH and GOPROXY environment variables. It then uses "go build" to compile the Go program.

details.comment: This code sets up a directory for dependencies, navigates to the MiraiGo folder, and configures the GOPATH and GOPROXY environment variables. It then uses "go build" to compile the Go program.
details.content:
#!/bin/bash
mkdir deps
cd MiraiGo
GOPATH=$PWD/../deps GOPROXY=https://goproxy.cn,direct go build
